&lt;li&gt;Experience trading liquid macro futures
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;`These will commonly include equity indices and/or metals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nice-to-have experience includes FX, crypto, options, and/or event-driven trading experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record independently managing a PnL, or being a senior member of the team, driving strategy in a larger environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior Proprietary Trading or Hedge Fund PM experience strongly preferred.
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Larger bank environment or similar experience may be considered if significant decision-making autonomy existed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Defined discretionary macro edge such as outcome distribution analysis, news and narrative interpretation, relative value frameworks, or portfolio construction discipline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Entrepreneurial mindset with competitive nature&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and interpersonal skills with the ability to work both autonomously and as a team player&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quant skills and data literacy are a plus but not required. Fully automated or black-box strategies are not the focus of this seat. Openness to feedback and willingness to adapt your trading style with changes in market conditions&lt;/li&gt;
